title: 'Le Bureau des Légendes' Season 5 and an Interview With Creator Éric Rochant
description:
Chris and Andy talk about the fifth and final season of 'Le Bureau des Légendes' and reflect on the series as a whole (1:00) before they are joined by creator Éric Rochant to talk about making the show (54:45).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Guest: Éric Rochant
Producer: Kaya McMullen
